      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL SNIPER (1) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (19.86) at Grafton in a Grade 3/4 over 350m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. HOTSHOT LILY (8) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 3.5 lengths (22.12) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Capable of going close again. FEDERAL SENOR (5) is a progressive type who recorded his 9th career win last time out (22.41) at The Gardens. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Hard to fault recent form and looks a key chance again.",
